org.openbel.framework.core.protonetwork
Interface ProtoNetworkExternalizer

All Known Implementing Classes:
BinaryProtoNetworkExternalizer, TextProtoNetworkExternalizer
public interface ProtoNetworkExternalizer

ProtoNetworkExternalizer represents an externalizable ProtoNetwork. This approach was necessary because the Externalizable and readObject/writeObject methods only supports a single output stream and the TextProtoNetworkExternalizer requires writing a ProtoNetwork to multiple table files.

Author:
Anthony Bargnesi <abargnesi@selventa.com>
